overview:
Computing is the UK’s leading business technology publication and a pioneering multimedia business-to-business brand. The title has been established for nearly 35 years and now extends across the widest portfolio of channels in its sector, covering print, internet, digital, email and PDA versions, plus web seminars, blogs, online video, podcasts, discussion forums, jobs, and the most successful awards programme in the UK IT industry.

Computing plays a vital role in keeping its readers up-to-date with the trends and issues that will inform their decisions on how to use technology for the benefit of their organisations.
